{"tid":423051,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ps4=大清 switch=太平天國","createTime":"2017-10-03T14:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T07:30:19.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9facce82c05e7b4551db3cc4d6b1fa03035f3d","tid":423051,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:57:31.000Z","msg":"Switch 版《FIFA 18》開賣無人吼<br />\n<br />\n《FIFA 18》日前正式上市，今年同步上市的版本共有 4 個，分別是 PS4、Xbox One、PC 和任天堂 Switch。當中 Switch 版是最讓開發者和玩家期待的，如果《FIFA 18》在這個新平台取得佳績，會令 EA 更有信心開發和推出更多遊戲，同時亦鼓勵其他遊戲商投放資源在 Switch 平台。<br />\n<br />\n《FIFA 18》Switch 版在推出前的試玩片段，獲得不少玩家和媒體正面評價，認為畫面質素不俗，遊戲流暢度亦高，原以為遊戲甫上市就會大賣，不過卻事與願違。有玩家陸續發現不同的 Bug 和問題，亦有玩家發現部份球員未有在遊戲中現身。由於上市時問題不少，據說《FIFA 18》已經令 Switch 玩家卻步，至今在英國售出的 Switch 版本只佔整體利潤的 1% 左右，銷量強差人意。<br />\n<br />\n開頭係威係勢，之後比人打到狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d42e717024234cfa13ccc13b2ac5e366ea4271","tid":423051,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37c7a6027f05521871bb9a430cb931046405e8c","tid":423051,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"任狗不願面對"},{"pid":"9939916a8ed22657e30d3cd7739f8cebb902497c","tid":423051,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"第一隻試水到出哂面，搵傻鳩買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8071605ea152e43fb8dadfe8fb8523de997eb22","tid":423051,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一隻試水到出哂面，搵傻鳩買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣得咁差,試完架啦,EA實無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 